            <p>2GB RAM<br>
i3 Procesor.<br>
500GB System memory<br>
Lenovo G500.<br>
I fixed it buy using console command: mat_dxlevel 90, mat_hdr_level 2, mat_hdr_enabled, mat_fullbright 0.<br>
it’s working fine, but every time when i enter game, need to type it in console command.</p>
