      <item>
        <title>Black Mesa: black/white textures, Bad Graphics</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[LordDz]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Looks like you’ve enabled fullbright.</p>
<p>So it’s the lighting you have trouble with, not the textures.</p>
<p>Try <a href="https://developer.valvesoftware.com/w/index.php?title=Mat_fullbright&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" data-bbcode="true" rel="nofollow noopener">mat_fullbright</a> 0 in the console.</p>
<ul>
<li>Is this one of the normal maps, you haven’t compiled it yourself in Hammer Editor?</li>
</ul>
